1
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:31,039
Hello.

2
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:31,680
Hello.

3
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,300
Is Boss Yuyao here?

4
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:37,240
Our boss went to Dinghai Shenzhen to fix something.

5
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,100
Fix something?

6
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:40,660
What is she fixing?

7
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:43,800
Cultivating.

8
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,320
Thanks.

9
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,120
Xuanqing.

10
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,520
Let's see what you do.

11
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,240
Master.

12
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,860
Help me move the stool.

13
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,920
I'll tidy up here.

14
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:42,880
Fatty, Skinny.

15
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:45,740
Skinny.

16
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,000
Fatty.

17
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,540
Want some naan?

18
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,329
What are you doing here?

19
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,120
I

20
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,900
came to see what you're doing.

21
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,160
You...

22
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:25,280
Why are you up there all by yourself?

23
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,600
I am up here alone.

24
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,640
Alone.

25
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,360
Did you remember something?

26
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:36,240
I think

27
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,440
I remembered

28
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,490
some fragments.

29
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,600
The two of us,

30
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,760
on horseback,

31
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:42,800
together,

32
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,240
galloping.

33
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:48,240
In the afterglow,

34
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,480
at sunset,

35
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,420
never leaving each other.

36
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,320
Probably,

37
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,840
I think,

38
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,010
it was like that.

39
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:05,840
Tell you what,

40
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,330
since you protected me well today,

41
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:11,250
I'll be your tour guide for the day.

42
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,290
Let's go.

43
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,120
What about this stool?

44
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,680
Leave it.

45
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,680
Someone will take care of it.

46
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,920
Let's go horseback riding.

47
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,640
Let's go.

48
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,600
Didn't you say

49
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,170
we're going horseback riding?

50
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,520
The horse

51
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,920
is on its way.

52
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,320
Let's first experience

53
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:36,720
this low-carbon, eco-friendly, and healthy little donkey.

54
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,320
Okay.

55
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,400
This e-bike

56
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,560
is pretty fast.

57
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:09,720
Is it good?

58
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,700
Let me introduce it to you.

59
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:16,640
Most of the things here

60
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,640
are cultural tourism derivatives.

61
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,840
Combining Kazakh traditional customs,

62
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:23,960
the legend of the Queen Mother of the West,

63
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,640
and the features of Tianshan Tianchi Lake,

64
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:28,570
many interesting creative products were designed.

65
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,440
Look.

66
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,260
This is the Mayashan Ropeway.

67
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,360
So comfortable.

68
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,520
Does it look good?

69
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,000
Yes.

70
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,640
The sunshine,

71
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,120
air,

72
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,980
and breeze here

73
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:03,440
all feel familiar.

74
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,120
It's like a dream.

75
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:06,810
When on earth

76
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,580
will this dream be unraveled?

77
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,000
Hey, handsome,

78
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,530
can you take a picture of us?

79
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,160
Okay.

80
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,930
One, two, three.

81
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,220
You can get closer.

82
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,960
One, two, three.

83
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,060
Looks good.

84
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,930
Does this look okay?

85
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:38,570
Looks great.

86
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,120
Thank you.

87
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,580
Thanks.

88
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,530
You're welcome.

89
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,159
What's wrong?

90
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,300
Is something on your mind?

91
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:51,960
No.

92
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,280
I just thought of a story.

93
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,960
It's not a love story, is it?

94
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,080
Am I that cliché?

95
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,840
It's a tragic love story.

96
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,530
Let me tell you about it.

97
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,800
A long time ago,

98
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,610
Tianchi was called Yaochi.

99
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,960
It is the bathing place of the Queen Mother.

100
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,920
On the east side is Dongxiao Tianchi,

101
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,120
also known as Feilong Pool.

102
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,080
It is where the Queen Mother washes her face.

103
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,880
On the west side is Xixiao Tianchi,

104
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,120
also known as Yunv Pool.

105
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,040
It is where the Queen Mother washes her feet.

106
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,720
One year,

107
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:23,120
the Queen Mother held a grand Peach Banquet

108
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,400
to entertain King Mu of Zhou, who came from afar.

109
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,800
Various immortals also kept them company.

110
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,120
However, the Queen Mother

111
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:31,560
forgot to invite the

112
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,280
flood dragons and water monsters at the bottom of Yaochi.

113
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:35,040
The water monster was very unhappy to hear this.

114
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,200
It wreaked havoc on the human world

115
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:38,530
and flooded everywhere to vent its anger.

116
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:41,040
The Queen Mother of the West was furious when she heard this.

117
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,120
She took out a jade hairpin from her hair

118
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,380
and put it in the water.

119
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,500
Yaochi immediately became calm.

120
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,040
As for that jade hairpin,

121
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:50,159
it's the elm tree you just saw.

122
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:52,800
We now call it the Needle that Calms the Sea.

123
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:58,480
To better guard that water-calming treasure,

124
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,770
the Queen Mother

125
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,940
specially sent a fairy down to the mortal realm.

126
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,380
Greetings, Queen Mother.

127
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:07,920
From today on,

128
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:10,240
you will manage Yaochi for me.

129
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,600
I grant you the name Yuyao.

130
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,160
You must not neglect your duties

131
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,440
or develop mortal affections.

132
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,040
Yuyao.

133
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,400
Thank you, Queen Mother.

134
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:25,800
I will guard the Jade Pool wholeheartedly,

135
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,860
and protect the Sea-calming Needle.

136
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,280
Time flies.

137
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,560
One day,

138
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,540
black mist rose from the tranquil Jade Pool.

139
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,760
The Sea-calming Needle showed abnormal movements,

140
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,560
which alarmed the Queen Mother.

141
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,840
After the Heavenly Court learned of this,

142
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,280
they dispatched a deity

143
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,400
to deal with it.

144
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,080
I wonder

145
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,080
which fellow cultivator is here.

146
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,280
Could you do me a favor

147
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,400
and let me

148
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,240
investigate this place?

149
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:57,720
Investigate?

150
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,040
What big words.

151
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:01,200
I am the boss here.

152
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,800
I watch over all the mountain spirits around here.

153
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,320
What kind of fellow cultivator are you?

154
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,520
Orders from above cannot be disobeyed.

155
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,210
Please understand, fairy.

156
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,520
You talk a big game,

157
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,620
but I wonder how your magic is.

158
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:14,780
How about this?

159
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,520
If you cannot break my formation

160
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,280
within the time an incense stick burns,

161
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,840
you should just go back.

162
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,240
Hey, big guy.

163
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,560
The incense is about to burn out.

164
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,340
Are you going to admit defeat?

165
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,320
So,

166
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:11,920
it's been that long.

167
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,520
I wanted

168
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,360
to sleep a little longer.

169
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:17,610
Then I'll start.

170
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,660
What are you doing?

171
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:40,960
Let me introduce myself.

172
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,560
I am

173
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,280
a heavenly official,

174
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,000
Lu Sinian.

175
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,490
Nice to meet you.

176
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,370
My name is Yuyao,

177
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,880
and I take care of Yaochi.

178
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,370
Nice to meet you,

179
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,060
Miss Yuyao.

180
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,650
I look forward to

181
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,080
working with you.
